OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA warm and
OL,6,Fsunny evening. Staying clear
OL,7,Fovernight, but the risk of some
OL,8,Fpatches of mist and fog forming once
OL,9,Fmore. A warm night for most.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FAny early fog clearing to
OL,12,Fleave a hot and sunny day across the
OL,13,Fcountry. Light winds and high UV
OL,14,Flevels expected. A very warm evening
OL,15,Fand night to come too.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FStaying
OL,18,Fdry, sunny and very warm throughout.
OL,19,FAn increased breeze may allow things
OL,20,Fto feel slightly cooler at times.
OL,21,FNights remaining warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
